title: WTF | Watch: Adorable Bulldog puppy encounters rain for the first time
text:
Fair warning: if you're any way inclined, this will make you seriously broody for a puppy.
This is Shelby, a 13-week-old English Bulldog puppy whose first encounter with rain was caught on camera by her owner and the interaction was, of course, so cute it hurts.
And if you're a fan of Shelby, and you should be, here's her first encounter with a GoPro which doesn't end well.
Via YouTube
